    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $("[id*=iframepressrealese]").load(function () {
                $(this).height($(this).contents().find("body").height());
            });
        });

        function Bind_PressReleaseDetails(PRID) {
            var filepath = "PressReleasePage.aspx?PRID=" + PRID;

            $("[id*=iframepressrealese]").attr("src", filepath);

            Bind_HashTag(PRID);
            Bind_HashTagReatedPost(PRID);
            var isMobile = window.matchMedia("only screen and (max-width: 767px)");
            if (isMobile.matches) {
                $("#bottomrel").attr("tabindex", -1).focus();                
            }
            return false;
        }

        function Bind_HashTag(PRID) {
            $.ajax(
            {
                type: "POST",
                url: "AjaxMethod.aspx/Get_HashTagList",
                data: '{PRID: "' + PRID + '" }',
                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                dataType: "json",
                success: OnSuccess,
                failure: function (response) {
                    alert(response.d);
                }
            });
        }
        function OnSuccess(response) {
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ltrTags').empty();
            if (JSON.parse(response.d).length > 0) {

                var varTag = "<ul>";
                varTag = varTag + "<h3>Tag</h3>";
                $.each(JSON.parse(response.d), function (idx, obj) {
                    varTag = varTag + "<li>" + "<a href='TagbasedSearch.aspx?Tag=" + obj.Hashtagstring + "'>" + obj.Hashtagstring + "</a></li>"
                });
                varTag = varTag + "</ul>";
                $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ltrTags').append(varTag);

            }


        }

        function Bind_HashTagReatedPost(PRID) {
            $.ajax(
            {
                type: "POST",
                url: "AjaxMethod.aspx/Bind_HasTagRelatePost",
                data: '{PRID: "' + PRID + '" }',
                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                dataType: "json",
                success: OnRelatedPostSuccess,
                failure: function (response) {
                    alert(response.d);
                }
            });
        }
        function OnRelatedPostSuccess(response) {
            $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ltrRefData').empty();
            if (JSON.parse(response.d).length > 0) {


                var varTag = "<ul>";
                varTag = varTag + "<h3>Similar Posts</h3>";
                $.each(JSON.parse(response.d), function (idx, obj) {
                    varTag = varTag + "<li>" + "<a href='PressReleseDetail.aspx?PRID=" + obj.PRID + "'>" + obj.Press_Title + "</a></li>"
                });
                varTag = varTag + "</ul>";
                $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_ltrRefData').append(varTag);
            }

        }

        function Bind_LeftMenuRealesd() {

            var varMinistryId = $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlMinistry").val();
            var varDay = $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlday").val();
            var varMonth = $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlMonth").val();
            var varYear = $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_ddlYear").val();
            var varRegion = 3;
            var varLang = 1;

            var data0 = { MinistryId: varMinistryId, Day: varDay, Month: varMonth, Year: varYear, Lang_ID: varLang, ReligionID: varRegion };
            $.ajax(
            {
                type: "POST",
                url: "AjaxMethod.aspx/Bind_LeftMenuRelease",
                data: '{p_releaseParam: ' + JSON.stringify(data0) + '}',
                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                dataType: "json",
                success: OnSuccessBind_LeftMenuRealesd,
                failure: function (response) {
                    alert(response.d);
                }
            });
        }
        function OnSuccessBind_LeftMenuRealesd(response) {

            if (JSON.parse(response.d).length > 0) {


            }

        }

    </script>
